Skills are reference directories — they contain instructions and resources, not executables.
BEFORE using any skill, you MUST:
1. Check if the skill's SKILL.md has already been read in this conversation (visible in your message history as a prior tool result). If yes, use the already-loaded content — do NOT read it again.
